...................................................
..................uploading........................
...................................................

well hopefully youve extracted this right
you should have the following files

------- evogb (folder)
--------------- images (sub dir)
--------------- languages (sub dir)
----------- readme
----------- guestbook.php
----------- connect.php // edit this one
----------- install.php
----------- header.php
----------- footer.php
----------- control.php // admin panel
----------- admin.php
----------- login.php
----------- post.php // javascript for smiles etc..
----------- vars.php 
----------- db_ (db types).php // 7 of these .. most common  = db_mysql.php


so when you upload you show called a folder 
called "evogb" with everything in there

note: you can put everything into the root directory of your web site and also
if you already have a footer.php and header.php you can use your ones instead of the ones supplied




...................................................
..............editing connect.php.....................
...................................................


just fill in your database details
username
password
data base name
data base type




...................................................
.................once edited.......................
...................................................

surf to http://yourdomain/evogb/install.php
once installed go to login.php

note : you do not have to delete the install.php after installation






and thats it really :)



